# Notes App (React)

## Overview
This is a simple notes application built with React. The app allows users to create, read, update, and delete notes.

## App Screenshots
![Notes App Home Screen](path/to/screenshot1.jpg)
*Home screen of the Notes App*

![Add Note Screen](path/to/screenshot2.jpg)
*Creating a new note*

## Features
- Create new notes
- View all notes
- Edit existing notes
- Delete notes
- Responsive design

## Technologies Used
- React
- CSS/SCSS
- Local Storage for data persistence

## Installation
1. Clone the repository
2. Run `npm install` to install dependencies
3. Run `npm start` to start the development server

## Usage
The app will open in your default browser at `http://localhost:3000`.